scripts.humanify-openai: for FILE in public/proprietary/*.js ; do npx humanifyjs openai "$FILE" && mv "output/deobfuscated.js" "output/$(basename $FILE)" ; done
scripts.humanify-gemini: for FILE in public/proprietary/*.js ; do npx humanifyjs gemini "$FILE" && mv "output/deobfuscated.js" "output/$(basename $FILE)" ; done
